Package infotrader.parser.validate

Classes that can validate the data in the object model for a variety of problems, so that the data written by the Writer is compliant with the GEDCOM standard.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DuplicateEliminator<T>
    A class to eliminate duplicate items from a { List}, while preserving the order of the List items.
    InfoTraderValidationFinding
    A class that holds information about something wrong with the gedcom data validated by { GedcomValidator}.
    InfoTraderValidator
    A class to validate the contents of a { InfoTrader} structure.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Severity
    The severity of a problem found during validation
